            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The Local Pack shows only the top 3 businesses directly in Google Search results. The Local Finder expands this to show all relevant businesses, typically 20 per page. Ranking factors are the same — GBP optimisation, reviews, citations, and proximity — but the Local Finder extends visibility to positions 4-20+.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Do Local Finder rankings differ from Local Pack rankings?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>They use the same signals but results can vary slightly. The Local Finder shows a fuller list and may show businesses ranked differently as the user pans the map, because distance calculations change with map position.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How do I rank higher in the Local Finder?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
